KATY PERRY PURPLE PRINT ON WHITE GILDAN SHIRTS. SUPER LIMITED TO ONLY 18.

The Twelve is a new, young London brand trying to do something new and exciting with our designs. Taking influence from hardcore, hip-hop and fashion culture/lifestyle, The Twelve is not an everyday t-shirt company. We’ll do our best to consistently come out with the freshest designs and the best quality apparel that we can. Everything will be super limited so don’t sleep on em.

Here’s to the future,
